The article is about the need to reform outdated immigration rules in order to bring the immigration system into the 21st century. President Donald J. Trump emphasizes the importance of closing loopholes that hinder common sense immigration enforcement. The article mentions that loopholes in the immigration system have contributed to the crisis at the border, particularly in relation to unaccompanied alien children (UAC) arrivals. Additionally, it highlights how loopholes in asylum laws have been exploited, leading to significant increases in asylum claims in recent years.